data.title: WTC Benches Offer a Fresh Start
data.meta_description: Newly installed benches outside the World Trade Center Oculus are more than places to sit. They represent opportunities to gain new skills and a new outlook for the eight formerly incarcerated individuals who built them through a unique partnership between the Port Authority and a Brooklyn non-profit.,Newly installed benches outside the World Trade Center Oculus are more than places to sit. They represent opportunities to gain new skills and a new outlook for the eight formerly incarcerated individuals who built them through a unique partnership between the Port Authority and a Brooklyn non-profit.
